name: DGN
attribute: DGN Diagnosis - specific combination of ICD-10 codes for primary and secondary as well multiple tumours if any

name: PRE5
attribute: PRE5 Volume that has been exhaled at the end of the first second of forced expiration - FEV1 (numeric)

name: PRE14
attribute: PRE14 T in clinical TNM - size of the original tumour, from OC11 (smallest) to OC14 (largest) (OC11,OC14,OC12,OC13)
